<b>Welcome to "in the Shell,"</b> a site dedicated to Ghost in the Shell (Kokaku kidotai) in all its incarnations, and to the philosophy found there.
<br><br>
This site was completely revamped in late January 2008 and is continuing to be updated with new reviews, images, and site tweaks.  For the latest info, see <a href="javascript:openNewWindow('whatsnew.html','thewin','height=450,width=510,toolbar=yes,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes')">What's New</a>.  For more technical info (such as browser compatibility), see the <a href="javascript:openNewWindow('versioninfo.html','thewin','height=450,width=510,toolbar=yes,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes')">version info</a>.  And, of course, see the menu above for all the articles, images, and other goodies!
<br><br>
Comments are welcome!  Just go to the <a href="http://www.neomythos.com/gitsphpBB">Discussion Boards</a> and jot down your thoughts.  You can also find a vast amount of info and commentary on Ghost in the Shell and many other subjects.
<br><br>
I hope you enjoy it!--Jeff
